    • registerPointPair

      public static void registerPointPair(@NonNull com.badlogic.gdx.utils.Json json)
      Registers PointPair with the given Json object, so PointPair can be written to and read from JSON. This does not automatically register the type of PointN used for each member of the PointPair. You may need to call registerCoord(Json) or use the default serializer for a point type.
      Parameters:
      json - a libGDX Json object that will have a serializer registered
